  "prompt": "What are the services provided by Five Boro Mold Specialist?",
  "response": "Five Boro Mold Specialist offers a range of services related to mold remediation and prevention. Here are the key services they provide:\n\n1. **Mold Inspection and Testing:**\n   - Comprehensive inspection of properties to identify mold growth.\n   - Air quality testing to detect mold spores and other contaminants.\n\n2. **Mold Removal and Remediation:**\n   - Safe and effective removal of mold from affected areas.\n   - Use of advanced techniques and equipment to ensure thorough remediation.\n\n3. **Water Damage Restoration:**\n   - Assessment and repair of water damage that can lead to mold growth.\n   - Drying and dehumidification services to prevent future mold issues.\n\n4. **Preventive Measures and Consulting:**\n   - Recommendations for preventing mold growth, including humidity control and ventilation improvements.\n   - Consulting services to help property owners maintain a mold-free environment.\n\n5. **Emergency Services:**\n   - 24/7 emergency response to address urgent mold and water damage issues.\n\n6. **Air Duct Cleaning:**\n   - Cleaning of HVAC systems to remove mold and improve indoor air quality.\n\nFive Boro Mold Specialist serves residential and commercial clients across the five boroughs of New York City, ensuring a safe and healthy living environment.",
